<template>
  Home
</template>

<script>
import axios from 'axios'
import { ref } from '@vue/reactivity';
export default {
  name: 'HomePage',
  setup() {
    let loginCheck = ref(true);
    axios.get('/api/').then(res=>{
      console.log(res.data);
      if(res.data === 'already login') {
        loginCheck.value = true;
      } else {
        loginCheck.value = false;
      }
      
    })
    
  }
}
</script>
